    caption: [A Portuguese man-of-war colony, *Physalia physalis* (order Siphonophora, class Hydrozoa). Colonies often drift onto southern ocean beaches, where a hazard to bathers. Each colony of medusa and polyp types is integrated to act as one individual. As many as 1000 zooids may be found in one colony. The nematocysts secrete a powerful neurotoxin.],
